Verification and Closure Status

All currently closed Phase 3 packs were closed using bounded verification appropriate to the environment.

That verification includes combinations of:

focused backend tests
focused frontend tests
build verification where relevant
route/render/code-path inspection
setup/runtime consistency checks
explicit bounded substitute acceptance records
explicit acknowledgement when live end-to-end manual chat/browser validation was not performed

The closures do not rely on pretending stronger validation than actually happened.

